This is my boathouse for the darkwood area :

features -

5 rooms
1 sailor- Krugan
items :
hidden key
hollow sword

Goal :
Find the key and give it to Krugan who gives you the hollow sword.You can
then enter the hole behind the chest where more info is given on how to
make your sword better.

This can be done by a potion and a waterspirit (not yet coded)

